              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The absolute cross sections are obtained at 600 MeV,",
                "from a known activation cross section for l2C into llC,",
                "to determine a ratio between a monitor detector",
                "and the beam current.",
                "At 1.2 and 2 GeV the cross sections are obtained from",
                "elastic-scattering yields from the H in a CH target",
                "combined with data (priv.comm. W.T.H.van Oers) from",
                "p + 3He at the same momentum transfer and",
                "                               similar c.m. energies."
              ]
